::Battera:;

She walked up and down the long corridoor of the ship.  She saw 
locked doors and a few open passageways.

She looked around and came to a small mass hall.  She walked up to 
the food dispencer.  She pressed a few buttons and out came a small 
bowl of fruits and berries.  She looked at the food.  She wasn't 
really hungry, but she knew she had to keep her strength up.  She 
took the bowl and walked down the hallway back towards her room.
She wasn't really happy with her assignment.  Sure it was easy 
enough. But she still had yet to talk to the leader.  And she was 
missing the company of Cybershark.

She opened the door to her room, stepped inside and closed the door 
behind her.
